know, I am not doing this with any theme in

00:09:04.730 --> 00:09:09.450
mind. I just think about it in the morning,
analyse and collect the threads by evening,

00:09:09.450 --> 00:09:14.450
record it at night, and publish it the next
morning. That is how it has been running along

00:09:14.450 --> 00:09:15.450
