00:09:15.450 --> 00:09:20.760
The same lady said, “Your contents are very
deep, profound, thanks!” I need to tell

00:09:20.760 --> 00:09:30.410
you something here. I am learning. I am not
just sharing what I know. For example, that

00:09:30.410 --> 00:09:40.380
Russian proverb that I shared with so much
“pride”, that proverb? I didn’t know.

00:09:40.380 --> 00:09:46.630
I didn’t know it until that afternoon! While
I was searching for something, I chanced upon

00:09:46.630 --> 00:09:53.590
this Russian proverb, and liking it, I decided
to share that with you all. That’s all.

00:09:53.590 --> 00:10:00.940
So, if I am doing Quotidians, there is a little
hidden agenda there. To learn something new

00:10:00.940 --> 00:10:09.230
